EXPECT A CIRCUS bumped with a rival at the start, was outpaced trailing while racing off the inside, was never near enough to threaten. PER THE HORSE RACING INTEGRITY AND SAFETY AUTHORITY, RUBY DOOBY DOO HAS BEEN DQ'D DUE TO A CROP VIOLATION.

ALLIWORSHIPNADORE broke outwardly, was forwardly-placed stalking from outside three to four wide, steadily weakened.
